sql_query.sql:
SELECT "groups"."id" FROM "groups" WHERE "groups"."id" = 125 AND (groups.id > 0) AND ( groups.id IN (
   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE members_visibility_level = 0

   UNION ALL

   SELECT id
     FROM groups
    WHERE members_visibility_level = 1
      AND NULL IS NOT NULL

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = NULL
    WHERE g.members_visibility_level = 2

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
LEFT JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = NULL AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.members_visibility_level = 3
      AND (gu.id IS NOT NULL OR FALSE)

   UNION ALL

   SELECT g.id
     FROM groups g
     JOIN group_users gu ON gu.group_id = g.id AND gu.user_id = NULL AND gu.owner
    WHERE g.members_visibility_level = 4
 )
) ORDER BY name ASC

SELECT "users"."id" FROM "users" INNER JOIN group_users ON group_users.user_id = users.id WHERE "users"."active" = TRUE AND "users"."staged" = FALSE AND (group_users.group_id IN (125)) AND (suspended_till IS NULL OR suspended_till <= '2020-05-28 18:58:07.535545') AND "users"."username_lower" = 'joecabot' LIMIT 20

SELECT "users"."id" FROM "users" LEFT OUTER JOIN "user_search_data" ON "user_search_data"."user_id" = "users"."id" INNER JOIN group_users ON group_users.user_id = users.id WHERE "users"."active" = TRUE AND "users"."staged" = FALSE AND (group_users.group_id IN (125)) AND (suspended_till IS NULL OR suspended_till <= '2020-05-28 18:58:07.541016') AND (user_search_data.search_data @@ TO_TSQUERY('simple', '''joecabot'':*')) ORDER BY CASE WHEN username_lower LIKE 'joecabot%' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ASC, last_seen_at DESC LIMIT 19
